---
// SignalRoutes — index.astro
// src/pages/index.astro
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SignalRoutes — Clear Signals. Better Decisions.</title>
<meta name="description" content="A suite of practical software tools helping founders, individuals, and organizations make clearer decisions — about money, business, news, and compliance.">
<meta property="og:title" content="SignalRoutes — Clear Signals. Better Decisions.">
<meta property="og:description" content="FounderRoutes · SpendScore · SourceBrief · ComplianceIQ — built by a founder, for founders.">
<meta property="og:url" content="https://signalroutes.work">
<meta property="og:image" content="/logo.png">
<link rel="icon" href="/logo.png">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
:root {
  --ink: #0e0e0e;
  --paper: #f5f2eb;
  --warm: #e8e2d5;
  --signal: #c8441a;
  --muted: #7a7468;
  --border: #d4cfc5;
  --green: #2a6e4a;
  --amber: #b87414;
  --blue: #1a4a7a;
}
body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); overflow-x: hidden; }

.app-logo    { width: 56px; height: 56px; object-fit: contain; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; border-radius: 10px; }
.app-logo-sm { width: 32px; height: 32px; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 6px; }
.nav-logo-img { height: 28px; object-fit: contain; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px; }

.scroll-progress { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--signal); width: 0%; z-index: 300; transition: width 0.1s linear; }

/* NAV */
nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 18px 48px;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 200;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: rgba(245,242,235,0.97);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
}
.nav-logo { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; display: flex; align-items: center; }
.nav-logo span { color: var(--signal); }
.nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; }

/* TABS */
.nav-tabs { display: flex; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
.nav-tab {
  padding: 9px 26px;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: none;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  border-right: 1.5px solid var(--border);
}
.nav-tab:last-child { border-right: none; }
.nav-tab:hover { background: var(--warm); color: var(--ink); }
.nav-tab.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }

.nav-cta {
  background: var(--signal);
  color: var(--paper);
  padding: 9px 22px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  white-space: nowrap;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: none;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }

/* TAB PANELS */
.tab-panel { display: none; }
.tab-panel.active { display: block; }

/* HERO */
.hero { min-height: 88vh; display: grid; grid-template-rows: 1fr auto; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 20%, rgba(200,68,26,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 10% 80%, rgba(42,110,74,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%); pointer-events: none; }
.hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px; opacity: 0.35; pointer-events: none; }
.hero-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 80px 48px 60px; position: relative; z-index: 5; max-width: 960px; }
.hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--signal); margin-bottom: 24px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s forwards; }
.hero-headline { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 7vw, 6.5rem); line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 28px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.35s forwards; }
.hero-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--signal); }
.hero-sub { font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 44px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.5s forwards; }
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.65s forwards; }
.btn-primary { background: var(--signal); color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: all 0.2s; border: 2px solid var(--signal); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: transparent; color: var(--signal); }
.btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 2px; border: 2px solid var(--border); font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; transition: all 0.2s; }
.btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }
.hero-stats { display: flex; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; z-index: 5; background: rgba(245,242,235,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.8s forwards; }
.stat-item { flex: 1; padding: 22px 48px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
.stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
.stat-num { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--ink); display: block; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
.stat-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-weight: 500; }

section { padding: 80px 48px; }
.section-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--signal); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.section-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem); letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 20px; }

/* ABOUT */
.about { background: #1a1a1a; color: var(--paper); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
.about .section-label { color: var(--signal); }
.about .section-title { color: var(--paper); }
.about-body { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.85); font-weight: 300; }
.about-body p + p { margin-top: 20px; }
.about-body strong { color: var(--paper); font-weight: 500; }
.about-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
.founder-card { border: 1px solid rgba(245,242,235,0.25); padding: 32px; border-radius: 2px; background: rgba(245,242,235,0.08); }
.founder-name { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.founder-title { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.6); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 16px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }
.founder-bio { font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.8); line-height: 1.6; }
.tag-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }
.tag { background: rgba(200,68,26,0.25); color: #f0a080; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

/* APPS */
.apps-section { background: var(--paper); }
.apps-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2px; margin-top: 60px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.app-card { background: var(--paper); padding: 48px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.3s; }
.app-card:hover { background: var(--warm); }
.app-card.middle { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.app-card.middle:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
.app-card.flagship { grid-column: span 2; border-right: none; background: var(--paper); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: start; gap: 60px; }
.app-card.flagship:hover { background: var(--warm); }
.flagship-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; padding-top: 8px; }
.flagship-stat { padding: 20px 24px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; background: var(--warm); }
.flagship-stat-num { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--signal); letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.flagship-stat-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.app-card.outlier { grid-column: span 2; border-bottom: none; border-right: none; background: var(--warm); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; align-items: center; gap: 40px; }
.app-num { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.app-name { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.app-tagline { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.5; }
.app-desc { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 300; }
.app-meta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
.status-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.06em; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
.status-live { background: #d4eade; color: var(--green); }
.status-beta { background: #fef3d4; color: var(--amber); }
.status-pipeline { background: #dce8f5; color: var(--blue); }
.status-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: currentColor; }
.price-tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 2px; }
.app-link { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--signal); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor; padding-bottom: 1px; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.app-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
.tab-link { background: none; border: none; color: var(--signal); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--signal); padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.tab-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
.outlier-badge { text-align: center; white-space: nowrap; }
.outlier-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.outlier-value { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--signal); display: block; }

/* TRACTION */
.traction { background: var(--warm); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.traction-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 48px; }
.traction-item { padding: 28px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; }
.traction-num { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; color: var(--signal); letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.traction-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.traction-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

/* ROADMAP */
.roadmap { background: var(--paper); }
.roadmap-paths { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; align-items: center; }
.path-card { padding: 24px 28px; border-radius: 2px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.path-organic { background: #f0f7f3; border-color: #b8d9c8; }
.path-accelerated { background: #fdf0eb; border-color: #f0c4b0; }
.path-label { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.path-desc { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
.path-divider { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--border); text-align: center; }
.roadmap-timeline { margin-top: 48px; position: relative; }
.roadmap-timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 120px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 1px; background: var(--border); }
.roadmap-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; position: relative; }
.roadmap-item + .roadmap-item { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.roadmap-date { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 28px 24px 28px 0; text-align: right; line-height: 1.4; }
.roadmap-content { padding: 28px 0 28px 40px; position: relative; }
.roadmap-content::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -4px; top: 36px; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); border: 2px solid var(--paper); }
.roadmap-item.active .roadmap-content::before { background: var(--signal); }
.roadmap-item.done   .roadmap-content::before { background: var(--green); }
.roadmap-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.roadmap-detail { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
.roadmap-revenue { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--signal); margin-top: 4px; }

/* INVEST */
.invest { background: #1a1a1a; color: var(--paper); }
.invest .section-label { color: var(--signal); }
.invest .section-title { color: var(--paper); }
.invest-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; margin-top: 60px; align-items: start; }
.invest-left p { font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.85); line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.invest-left strong { color: var(--paper); font-weight: 500; }
.needs-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 32px; }
.needs-list li { display: flex; gap: 16px; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,242,235,0.15); }
.needs-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.need-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
.need-title { font-weight: 500; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
.need-desc { font-size: 0.83rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.7); line-height: 1.55; }
.contact-card { border: 1px solid rgba(245,242,235,0.25); padding: 40px; background: rgba(245,242,235,0.07); }
.contact-card h3 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.contact-card > p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.7); margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.6; }
.contact-options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
.contact-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding: 16px 20px; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid rgba(245,242,235,0.2); border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.2s; background: rgba(245,242,235,0.05); }
.contact-btn:hover { background: rgba(200,68,26,0.2); border-color: var(--signal); }
.contact-btn-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.contact-btn-text strong { display: block; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--paper); font-weight: 500; }
.contact-btn-text span { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.6); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }
.contact-btn.highlight { background: rgba(200,68,26,0.15); border-color: var(--signal); }
.deck-banner { margin-top: 24px; padding: 18px 20px; border: 1px dashed rgba(200,68,26,0.45); border-radius: 2px; background: rgba(200,68,26,0.06); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
.deck-banner-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.deck-banner-text strong { display: block; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--paper); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.deck-banner-text span { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(245,242,235,0.55); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

footer { padding: 40px 48px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.footer-logo { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--muted); display: flex; align-items: center; }
.footer-logo span { color: var(--signal); }
.footer-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s; }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  nav { padding: 14px 20px; }
  .nav-right { gap: 12px; }
  .nav-tab { padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 0.72rem; }
  .nav-cta { padding: 7px 14px; font-size: 0.72rem; }
  section { padding: 52px 24px; }
  .hero-body { padding: 52px 24px 40px; }
  .hero-stats { flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .stat-item { padding: 16px 20px; flex: 1 1 50%; }
  .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .apps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .app-card.flagship { grid-column: span 1; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
  .app-card.outlier { grid-column: span 1; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .app-card.middle:nth-child(2) { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .traction-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .roadmap-paths { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .path-divider { display: none; }
  .roadmap-timeline::before { left: 72px; }
  .roadmap-item { grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr; }
  .invest-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scroll-progress" id="scrollProgress"></div>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <img src="/logo.png" alt="SignalRoutes" class="nav-logo-img">Signal<span>Routes</span>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <div class="nav-tabs">
      <button class="nav-tab active" data-tab="story">Our Story</button>
      <button class="nav-tab" data-tab="opportunity">The Opportunity</button>
    </div>
    <button class="nav-cta" id="connectCta">Let's Connect</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ TAB 1: OUR STORY ═══════════════════════════ -->
<div class="tab-panel active" id="tab-story">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">SignalRoutes · Pacific Northwest · Est. 2025</div>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">Tools that cut<br>through the <em>noise.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">A suite of practical software products helping founders, individuals, and organizations make clearer decisions — about money, business, news, and compliance.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#products" class="btn-primary">Explore Products</a>
        <button class="btn-ghost" data-switchtab="opportunity">The Opportunity →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">4</span><span class="stat-label">Products in portfolio</span></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">3</span><span class="stat-label">States launched · WA · CA · NY</span></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">10+</span><span class="stat-label">Beta testers active</span></div>
      <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-num">Apr '26</span><span class="stat-label">SpendScore Play Store launch</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label reveal">The Story</div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Built by a founder,<br>for founders.</h2>
      <div class="about-body reveal">
        <p>SignalRoutes was born out of a simple frustration: <strong>too much noise, not enough signal.</strong> Starting and running a business in the Pacific Northwest meant navigating a maze of regulations, financial tools, and information sources — none of them designed to work together.</p>
        <p>So we built the tools we wished existed. Each product in the SignalRoutes portfolio solves a real, specific problem — and together they form a system for <strong>clearer thinking and better decisions</strong> across every stage of business and personal growth.</p>
        <p>Bootstrapped, profitable-path focused, and building in public from the Pacific Northwest.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-right reveal">
      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-name">Laile Fletcher</div>
        <div class="founder-title">Founder · Developer · Operator</div>
        <div class="founder-bio">Solo founder building a portfolio of practical SaaS tools from the Pacific Northwest. Background spanning fintech compliance, small business operations, and software development. Every product is built, tested, and shipped by someone who uses it.</div>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">Bootstrapped</span>
          <span class="tag">Pacific NW</span>
          <span class="tag">SaaS</span>
          <span class="tag">Solo Founder</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="apps-section" id="products">
    <div class="section-label reveal">The Portfolio</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Proof of execution.<br><em style="color:var(--signal);">Then the opportunity.</em></h2>
    <div class="apps-grid reveal">

      <div class="app-card middle">
        <div class="app-num">01 · Live &amp; Shipping</div>
        <img src="/spendscore.png" alt="SpendScore" class="app-logo">
        <div class="app-name">SpendScore</div>
        <div class="app-tagline">Understand your money in real time.</div>
        <div class="app-desc">A mobile-first personal finance app that scores your spending behavior and builds better financial habits over time. Launching on Google Play mid-April 2026 — available in the US, EU, and Canada. Monetized via subscription and AdMob ad revenue.</div>
